Class DatasetTrainer<M extends Model,L>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.ml.trainers.DatasetTrainer<M,L>
  • Type Parameters:
    M - Type of a produced model.
    L - Type of a label.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BaggingModelTrainer, DecisionTree, GDBTrainer, MultiLabelDatasetTrainer, RandomForestTrainer, SingleLabelDatasetTrainer

    public abstract class DatasetTrainer<M extends Model,L>
extends Object
    Interface for trainers. Trainer is just a function which produces model from the data.
